stories.title: Rain washes out Zimbabwe's hopes
stories.subTitle: West Indies v Zimbabwe, 6th ODI, Trinidad
stories.summary: It was rain which set up the opportunity for Zimbabwe to snatch an improbable victory in the sixth ODI at Trinidad's Queen's Park Oval, but it also ultimately washed out that hope
